room_title: Escape room "The Fortune Teller" by The Escape Room Experience in Laconia
room_address: 555 Main Street Suite A Laconia, NH 03246
room_description: Madame Kezia is a traveling gypsy who makes a fortune scamming naive customers desperate for answers about their future. You and your friends decide to pay her a visit hoping to prove once and for all that she is a fraud. But something goes terribly wrong. Madame Kezia’s Tarot cards have accidentally opened a passageway to the other side. Now you’re all in the fight of your lives to save your souls from slipping through to the other side for eternity. Ghostly voices, thunder and lightning, this is not a mission for the faint of heart. Can you save your souls before they are lost forever?
